snippet.title: FPL Family
snippet.description:
Join husband and wife duo Lee and Sam on our weekly live streams discussing all things Fantasy Premier League (FPL)!

On Sunday nights (8:30pm GMT), we react to the FPL Gameweek and share our scores and ranks for the week. Keep up to date with other members of the FPL Community in our weekday 'FPL Family x' videos and catch the live stream highlights every Tuesday, right here on the Channel.

Like, subscribe and share!
